ensity regions of the universe and that fossil galaxies represent the end\nproducts of galaxy mergers in groups and clusters. The online FS catalog can be\nfound at http://www.astro.ljmu.ac.uk/~xcs/Harrison2012/XCSFSCat.html.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 20 Feb 2012 20:59:14 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 26 Jul 2012 16:01:21 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-04"}
